            <div class="lp-plan-tile__header-icon lp-plan-tile__tooltip-trigger"> 
             <img loading="lazy" src="https://s1.wp.com/wp-content/themes/h4/assets/pricing/woo-logo.svg" alt="Entrepreneur"> <span class="lp-plan-tile__tooltip"> Make your online store a reality with the power of WooCommerce. </span> 
