       <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-large-font-size">Think WordPress isn’t for the enterprise? Think&nbsp;again.</h2> 
       <p>What do Salesforce, Al Jazeera, Capgemini, and Facebook have in common?</p> 
       <p>They trust WordPress VIP—the enterprise platform built on WordPress—to deliver performance at scale while meeting the highest security standards. Starting at $25,000/year.<a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://wpvip.com/wordpress-vip-agile-content-platform?utm_source=WordPresscom&amp;utm_medium=automattic_referral&amp;utm_campaign=lohp" target="_blank"></a></p> 
