    <div class="instructions" data-platform="mac-os">
     <ol>
      <li>Open System Preferences.</li>
      <li>Search for <strong>DNS Servers</strong> and select it from the dropdown.</li>
      <li>Click the <strong>+</strong> button to add a DNS Server and enter <strong class="code">1.1.1.1</strong></li>
      <li>Click <strong>+</strong> again and enter <strong class="code">1.0.0.1</strong> (This is for redundancy.)</li>
      <li>Click <strong>+</strong> again and enter <strong class="code">2606:4700:4700::1111</strong> (This is for redundancy.)</li>
      <li>Click <strong>+</strong> again and enter <strong class="code">2606:4700:4700::1001</strong> (This is for redundancy.)</li>
      <li>Click <strong>Ok</strong>, then click <strong>Apply</strong>.</li>
      <li>You’re all set! Your device now has faster, more private DNS servers ✌️✌️</li>
     </ol><stream style="width: 616px; max-width: 100%;" src="b95943849d53350130ba22d039fa6faf" controls="">
